OL,3,CImam 'terrified' after finding pork
OL,4,Cand Israeli flag outside entrance to
OL,5,Cmosque
OL,7,FAn imam has described being left
OL,8,F"terrified" after discovering pork and
OL,9,Fan Israeli flag outside the entrance
OL,10,Fto a mosque in Oxford.
OL,12,FImam Shaykh Sahibzada Jamil Khan was
OL,13,Falone at Oxford Central Mosque when he
OL,14,Ffound the "disturbing items".
OL,16,FThe imam said as he opened the main
OL,17,Fdoor he smelt raw meat.
