OL,3,CImam 'terrified' after finding pork
OL,4,Cand Israeli flag outside entrance to
OL,5,Cmosque
OL,7,F"I looked around and noticed that
OL,8,Fsomeone had stuck what seemed to be
OL,9,Fpork on the mosque candles and an
OL,10,FIsraeli flag at the middle of the
OL,11,Fmosque entrance," he said.
OL,13,F"Straight away, I spoke to the
OL,14,Fmanagement, called 999 and we went
OL,15,Ffrom there."
OL,17,FHe added: "I was the only person in
OL,18,Fthe mosque, so I was terrified and I
OL,19,Fwas upset.
