OL,3,CImam 'terrified' after finding pork
OL,4,Cand Israeli flag outside entrance to
OL,5,Cmosque
OL,7,F"For a Muslim, religion means
OL,8,Feverything, so being the leader of the
OL,9,FMuslim community, it was quite
OL,10,Fdisturbing.
OL,12,F"We're lost for words."
OL,14,FAsked whether people are frightened he
OL,15,Fsaid: "The elders are always going to
OL,16,Fbe vulnerable, so we do feel for our
OL,17,Felders because they've put very hard
OL,18,Fwork and dedication for the mosque to
OL,19,Fbe where it is now.
