OL,4,Cand Israeli flag outside entrance to
OL,5,Cmosque
OL,7,F"For them, it's a time where they
OL,8,Fshould be relaxing, enjoying and
OL,9,Fseeing the fruits of their efforts,
OL,10,Fbut for them to be scared coming to
OL,11,Fthe mosque is upsetting."
OL,13,FFlowers and letters from different
OL,14,Fcommunities including the Christian
OL,15,Fcommunity and the Jewish community
OL,16,Fhave been sent to the mosque as a show
OL,17,Fof support.
