OL,7,F"That's given us somewhat confidence
OL,8,Fand support we need, so we appreciate
OL,9,Feverybody's help," Imam Shaykh
OL,10,FSahibzada Jamil Khan said.
OL,12,F"There is no reason for it to happen
OL,13,Fand we don't know why it's happened,
OL,14,Fespecially because we as a community
OL,15,Fhaven't done anything to anyone."
OL,17,FOn Friday 22 August, people gathered
OL,18,Fat the mosque, coming together in a
OL,19,Fshow of solidarity.
