OL,7,FThames Valley Police Chief
OL,8,FSuperintendent Ben Clark said: "This
OL,9,Fwas a provocative act to upset and
OL,10,Foffend mosque users.
OL,12,F"Such behaviour has no place in our
OL,13,Fcommunity and we will do everything in
OL,14,Four powers to bring anybody involved
OL,15,Fto justice.
OL,17,F"An active investigation is ongoing
OL,18,Fwith a number of lines of enquiry that
OL,19,Fare being progressed by detectives.
